Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.09,0:00:16.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs22}廢墟是現代的秘境！！  男人的浪漫！！！來吧  同志們！！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.70,0:00:34.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs22}白鳥座
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.41,0:00:39.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,海報一點作用都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.80,0:00:41.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,到現在廢墟研的部員還是3人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.90,0:00:44.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,再這麼發展下去就是廢墟研的滅亡危機了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.50,0:00:46.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在暑假裡想想對策吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.18,0:00:49.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我又不是廢墟研的…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.25,0:00:50.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,千川
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.67,0:00:55.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為了配合中學時代性格陰沉的你的愛好  才迷上廢墟的我們
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.34,0:00:57.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你不覺得有責任嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.65,0:00:58.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,關我啥事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.06,0:01:02.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,既然這樣不如做一段印象影片吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.70,0:01:05.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,廢墟的影像配上音樂
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.57,0:01:06.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,影片？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.68,0:01:07.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哦  這主意不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.54,0:01:10.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我的電腦就可以做
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.77,0:01:11.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就它了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.30,0:01:13.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  問題是資金啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.95,0:01:18.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這附近沒有能吸引新人的廢墟
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.52,0:01:20.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,交通費和住宿費？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.60,0:01:21.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.60,0:01:23.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,拍攝需要時間
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.50,0:01:25.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,1天內是弄不完的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.31,0:01:27.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,即使不做那麼正式的東西…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.01,0:01:28.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.99,0:01:33.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在我們廢墟研存亡的時刻  不盡全力怎麼行
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.35,0:01:36.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,都說了我不是廢墟研…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.78,0:01:40.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,千川  你這傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.61,0:01:41.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.99,0:01:43.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,中杉同學  你在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.99,0:03:22.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你可真有福氣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.10,0:03:26.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,又不是乘坐豪華遊輪周遊世界
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.33,0:03:29.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼  就是說你在悠閒享受的期間
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.50,0:03:32.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要我一個人看家？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.85,0:03:36.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,倒垃圾  打掃  採購  全部都
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.13,0:03:41.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你自己擅自回來的  沒理由這樣抱怨吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.27,0:03:46.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,難得的暑假  比起待在公寓狹窄憋屈的房間裡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.86,0:03:50.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我更想在寬敞  懷念  舒適的自己家休息
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.04,0:03:53.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這才是人之常情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.77,0:03:55.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,才3天有什麼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.82,0:03:58.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你這是求人的態度嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.43,0:04:00.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是過暑假啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.45,0:04:00.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.65,0:04:04.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託你了  姐姐大人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.27,0:04:06.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼「姐姐大人」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.07,0:04:08.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,求您務必…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.84,0:04:12.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也好  真沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.66,0:04:13.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.62,0:04:15.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,作為交換
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.37,0:04:20.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等你回來後  暑假期間的倒垃圾  購物全歸你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.25,0:04:21.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只有洗衣服除外
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.53,0:04:25.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,該死的羽津美  總是抓我的弱點
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.36,0:04:28.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒辦法嘛  你想去旅行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.23,0:04:32.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,廢話  難得中杉同學邀請我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.39,0:04:35.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀哎呀  全力發情中
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.18,0:04:36.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不許說發情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.48,0:04:39.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真的可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.46,0:04:43.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小夜香說她想去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.57,0:04:46.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有你在她身邊沒什麼好擔心的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.34,0:04:48.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,既然老爺您這麼說…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.10,0:04:51.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小夜香好不容易變得有精神了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.73,0:04:53.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就隨她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.91,0:04:54.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.31,0:05:08.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,該死的羽澤  叛徒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.85,0:05:10.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,回去就制裁他
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.29,0:05:14.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒什麼嘛  須藤和千明都在
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.69,0:05:18.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是嘛  難得他中了張秋葉LIVE的票
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.73,0:05:20.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我沒中啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.72,0:05:23.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可那個笨蛋卻中了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.43,0:05:24.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  我知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.96,0:05:27.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,難得來一趟  開心點嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.46,0:05:30.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對  對  就像小良所說
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.55,0:05:33.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小和  去拍中杉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.81,0:05:34.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,拍出來肯定不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.34,0:05:37.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,早宮  稍微讓一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.61,0:05:38.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.44,0:05:40.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我們要拍中杉的影片
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.61,0:05:41.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你礙著我們了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.32,0:05:43.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.06,0:05:46.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,拍到你就不算「窗邊美女」了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.24,0:05:47.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  快點讓開
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.94,0:05:50.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,美女的話這邊也有吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.23,0:05:51.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,來  拍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.72,0:05:54.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,想要我擺什麼Pose可以說哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.00,0:05:56.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小和  動下攝影機
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.10,0:05:59.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,把這個誇張妄想的女人從鏡頭裡除掉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.30,0:06:17.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  這裡是鈴木家
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.31,0:06:19.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我是小夜香  我們剛到車站
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.02,0:06:21.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,麻煩您準備好食物
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.69,0:06:23.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大家肚子都餓扁了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.54,0:06:25.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那我去準備車子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.11,0:06:27.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我們坐公車來  就不麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.20,0:06:29.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,公車嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.30,0:06:32.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  那麼一會見
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.15,0:06:43.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.46,0:06:44.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,連個便利店都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.18,0:06:47.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真的呢  好安靜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.12,0:06:49.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,都有點嚇人了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.05,0:06:56.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  是那個吧  中杉同學
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.02,0:06:59.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  對對  我想起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.49,0:07:03.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我小時候還是個很豪華的旅館的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.49,0:07:06.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但在很久以前因經營不善倒閉了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.32,0:07:11.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然把溫泉作為賣點  但國道修在了山那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.52,0:07:13.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,來的人就越來越少了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.91,0:07:15.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這真是個不錯的廢墟啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.11,0:07:18.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,男人的心被吸引了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.57,0:07:25.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,被吸引了…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.37,0:07:25.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,煩死啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.79,0:07:28.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,婆婆  有洋芋片嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.18,0:07:30.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,洋芋片？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.36,0:07:32.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  他是指Potato Chips
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.61,0:07:37.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  那我去裡面拿  嘿咻
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.63,0:07:39.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,稍等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.37,0:07:41.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個  請您快一點
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.21,0:07:42.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,公車的發車時間快…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.94,0:07:47.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只要拜託司機就會多等一會的  不用擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.30,0:07:51.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還有  要一打碗麵
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.69,0:07:52.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.37,0:07:54.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起  早宮
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.03,0:07:55.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.71,0:07:57.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,讓你替我擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.39,0:08:00.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我沒有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.41,0:08:04.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,每次我擦汗的時候  你就擔心似地看著我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.44,0:08:11.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因為他們都是男生  不會去細心注意別人的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.58,0:08:13.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,超重啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.34,0:08:15.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  煩死了  不是都分好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.79,0:08:17.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小良  別吵架啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.80,0:08:20.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過  好像是沒問題了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.74,0:08:24.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我覺得身體很輕鬆  所以別擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.39,0:08:27.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎  身體真的變得好了呢  中杉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.48,0:08:47.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,到啦  到啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.06,0:08:48.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,到達啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.71,0:08:49.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋  吵死啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.90,0:08:52.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那邊的就是我家的別墅
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.74,0:08:54.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要走到那麼遠嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.33,0:08:54.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.09,0:08:57.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好啦  出發
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.90,0:09:06.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在我小的時候  這個村子更有活力的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.86,0:09:08.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,孩子們也很多
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.58,0:09:09.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所謂人口稀少化吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.16,0:09:12.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好像年輕人都出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.99,0:09:15.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我也7年沒來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.73,0:09:29.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,良枝阿姨
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.00,0:09:37.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,吃飽啦  吃飽啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.49,0:09:41.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,飯菜真是出乎意料得好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.88,0:09:45.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,想想明天的安排  也該稍微控制一下嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.37,0:09:48.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你不也加了3碗嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.55,0:09:49.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我要吃2人份…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.69,0:09:51.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,2人份？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.03,0:09:56.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我只吃了2人份  須藤可吃了3人份
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.96,0:09:58.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,五十步笑百步
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.90,0:10:03.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個傭人婆婆  雖然表情嚴肅  菜做得倒是不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.33,0:10:07.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,河的上游  無人居住的民宅到處都是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.88,0:10:10.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這一帶簡直是廢墟的寶庫
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.19,0:10:14.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,待會叫上早宮和中杉打牌吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.62,0:10:16.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大家在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.84,0:10:19.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,中杉說要給大家看個好東西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.02,0:10:30.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哦  銀河好清晰
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.90,0:10:34.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,空氣清澄  加上附近基本上沒有燈光
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.37,0:10:40.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這個是？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.39,0:10:43.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,爺爺用這個觀察鳥類
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.46,0:10:44.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.26,0:10:46.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,能看到什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.47,0:10:47.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看了就知道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.80,0:10:52.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哇  真漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.65,0:10:55.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼呀  千川  讓我也看看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.25,0:10:58.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也讓我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.39,0:10:58.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,煩人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.69,0:11:01.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,讓我看  讓我看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.10,0:11:03.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我是下一個
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.21,0:11:04.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你這傢伙  放開我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.34,0:11:05.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,放不開啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.18,0:11:05.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,叫你放開
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.92,0:11:08.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你們是小學的小鬼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.88,0:11:10.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過  也讓我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.95,0:11:12.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那我就先了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.03,0:11:14.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,叫你放開
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.09,0:11:15.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,讓我也看看嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.28,0:11:17.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,礙事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.72,0:11:19.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼漂亮的星星我還是第一次見
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.23,0:11:21.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,白鳥座β星
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.03,0:11:23.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,叫做albideo的星星
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.91,0:11:27.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,中杉同學對星星很瞭解嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.33,0:11:30.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我從小體弱多病
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.76,0:11:33.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,自然而然的喜歡上了仰望星空
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.32,0:11:39.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那顆星雖然看著很近  其實很遠的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.97,0:11:40.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,多少公里？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.68,0:11:45.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是地球距太陽的4千倍左右
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.93,0:11:48.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大概是6千億公里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.33,0:11:51.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,6千億公里嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.46,0:11:53.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,讓我看看嘛  喂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.11,0:11:56.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,叫你放手
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.58,0:11:57.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哇  真漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.29,0:11:59.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你們倆適可而止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.81,0:12:08.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是不錯的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.08,0:12:10.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,拍得怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.58,0:12:11.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,很完美
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.05,0:12:14.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  接下來就是今天的主要項目了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.98,0:12:16.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在此之前
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.16,0:12:17.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼  開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.05,0:12:19.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.50,0:12:21.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,畢竟是昨天定的規矩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.87,0:12:23.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,最初是布
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.91,0:12:25.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,剪子石頭布
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.15,0:12:27.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不分勝負
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.10,0:12:28.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,勝負…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.15,0:12:29.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,勝負…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.63,0:12:38.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡的書你喜歡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.35,0:12:40.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  都是些很棒的書
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.59,0:12:43.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,照片集什麼的  印刷和裝訂都很出色
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.67,0:12:44.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.93,0:12:47.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你不喜歡這一類？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.16,0:12:49.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有點
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.28,0:12:52.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看來中杉不喜歡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.34,0:12:53.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,報道照片
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.48,0:12:55.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不說這個  我們到下面去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.76,0:12:58.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,良枝阿姨為我們準備了冷飲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.95,0:13:00.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.23,0:13:02.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我正好口渴呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.47,0:13:06.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,說起來我是不是應該跟他們一塊去的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.56,0:13:10.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那旅館是禁止入內的  被發現了可就麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.35,0:13:13.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那幫傢伙的話應該有對策吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.75,0:13:16.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小和  能聽到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.71,0:13:17.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.34,0:13:19.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒問題  小良
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.08,0:13:21.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我用了兩根天線
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.67,0:13:26.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼響3聲後掛斷  這樣作為暗號如何
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.47,0:13:28.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  3聲對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.61,0:13:31.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要是見到什麼有趣的東西也給我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.18,0:13:34.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了啦  那就這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.12,0:13:37.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼開始探險
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.20,0:13:44.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哇哈哈  化石遊戲的寶庫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.84,0:13:47.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  千明  照明  照明
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.43,0:13:50.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  就像是時間穿越一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.78,0:13:53.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這些東西擺在這裡  不覺得有點恐怖氣氛嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.80,0:13:57.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡  要拍的太多  我有點迷茫
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.28,0:13:59.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,千明  暫時保持照明
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.46,0:14:00.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好  好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.58,0:14:03.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,千川  你先去樓上調查
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.71,0:14:05.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,快點  快點
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.45,0:14:06.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.53,0:14:18.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  為什麼是我把風啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.32,0:14:21.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.81,0:14:30.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你是來旅行的？沒見過你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.59,0:14:34.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,風光明媚就是指這樣的地方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.54,0:14:37.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呀  真是個美麗的村莊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.79,0:14:38.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.16,0:14:46.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,暴露沒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.94,0:14:50.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不行  還不能被發現
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.86,0:14:56.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  走了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.90,0:14:59.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,Safe
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.50,0:15:05.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,千川  警戒警報解除
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.71,0:15:08.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我看到了  沒想到須藤竟然能蒙混過去…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.30,0:15:11.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.75,0:15:14.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  千川  能聽見嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.03,0:15:17.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,回答我  喂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.10,0:15:20.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定是惡作劇
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.18,0:15:26.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在棍子一端綁上鞋子  那種腳印很容易弄出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.09,0:15:27.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,或許吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.20,0:15:29.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過還真有點嚇人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.34,0:15:31.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可能是幽靈吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.76,0:15:32.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.86,0:15:35.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才的警官說的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.34,0:15:39.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天晚上  這附近聽到了小孩的笑聲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.44,0:15:41.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但卻四下無人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.00,0:15:45.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小良  別說了  我最怕這種東西了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.31,0:15:46.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你可真膽小啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.66,0:15:48.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小良  你身後
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.38,0:15:51.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,幽靈  好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.87,0:15:52.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這傢伙怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.04,0:15:54.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我怕幽靈
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.02,0:15:56.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.08,0:15:58.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,又來  煩死啦  放開我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.30,0:15:59.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.28,0:16:36.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,快點睜開眼睛  硫加
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.19,0:16:39.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不對  我…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.48,0:16:43.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你重生了  小夜香
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.44,0:16:45.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就像你希望的那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.68,0:16:48.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我希望的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.41,0:16:52.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對吧  所以硫加才選擇了你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.14,0:16:53.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,被選中？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.51,0:16:56.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對  你也是那麼期望的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.29,0:17:02.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我才…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.42,0:17:18.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼啊  死了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.44,0:17:23.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這傢伙還活著
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.39,0:17:29.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,硫加
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.57,0:17:33.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,硫加依靠你的力量  從長久的睡眠中覺醒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.26,0:17:39.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你也依靠硫加的力量  獲得了新生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.99,0:17:41.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,硫加
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.72,0:17:50.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,來  飛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.35,0:17:53.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,硫加
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.64,0:18:15.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,弗拉提  安靜點行不
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.78,0:18:17.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這狗真沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.03,0:18:22.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,吃那麼多還不聽我的話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.98,0:18:36.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這感覺是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.43,0:18:44.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,中杉小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.87,0:18:46.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你在做什麼  巴迪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.05,0:18:48.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我還睏著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.92,0:18:50.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那你就接著睡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.70,0:18:56.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  巴迪  怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.28,0:18:59.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.11,0:19:01.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.22,0:19:01.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,別問了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.66,0:19:05.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,去哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.75,0:19:07.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,巴迪  到底怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.59,0:19:26.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,又來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.80,0:19:27.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,巴迪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.86,0:19:47.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.38,0:19:53.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,巴迪  那是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.00,0:20:18.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然長野縣政府和公務員盡全力展開救援行動及調查
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.66,0:20:22.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但澤尻村是典型的人口稀少型村落
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.38,0:20:24.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,難以確保移動手段
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.72,0:20:27.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,正在商討是否出動自衛隊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.56,0:20:32.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs22}因此  至今還未展開對生存者的調查
